<div>
	<label>Please list up to five academic awards that you have received (e.g. Award - Date Received [mm/yy])</label><br />
	<%= e.awards.blank? || e.awards.size <= 4 ? "You have not added any academic awards." :  e.awards %>
</div>
<br style="clear:both;"/>

<div>
	<label>Do you feel your GPA accurately reflects your academic abilities?  Please comment on why or why not in the space provided:</label><br style="clear:both;"/>
	<%= e.gpa_comments.blank? || e.gpa_comments.size <= 4 ? "You have not answered this question." : e.gpa_comments %>
</div>
<br style="clear:both;"/>

<div>
	<label>How did you learn about Research Experience for Undergrads (REU)?</label><br />
	<%= e.learn ? e.learn : "You have not answered this question." %>
</div>
<br style="clear:both;"/>

<div>
	<label>Please list any computer skills:</label><br />
	<%= e.comp_skills.blank? || e.comp_skills.size <= 4 ? "You have not added any computer skills." : e.comp_skills %>
</div>
<br style="clear:both;"/>

<div>
	<label>Please describe all system building experiences you have had. This could be for example working with robotics, embedded software (e.g. Arduino), electronics, machining, etc. (up to 200 words).:</label><br />
	<%= e.lab_skills.blank? ||  e.lab_skills.size <= 4 ? "You have not added any lab skills." : e.lab_skills %>
</div>
<br style="clear:both;"/>

<div>
	<label>Please Complete a brief essay (up to 250 words) explaining why you are interested in our program and how the experience may help you achieve your future goals:</label>
	<%= e.personal_statement.blank? || e.personal_statement.size <= 4 ? "You must complete your personal statement." : e.personal_statement %>
</div>
